<title>Four Operations in Math</title>
<h1>Hello World!</h1>
<h2>Four Operations in Math</h2>
<h2>In the first form, enter a list of integers separated by a newline character</h2>
<h2>In the second form, enter first integer value</h2>
<h2>In the third form, enter second integer value</h2>
<h2>In the last form, select the operation type</h2>
<h2>Result is {{result}}</h2>

<form action="compute" method="post">
    <textarea name="input1" rows="10" cols="30" required></textarea>
    <textarea name="input2" rows="10" cols="30" required></textarea>
    <textarea name="input3" rows="10" cols="30" required></textarea>
    <select name="input4">
        <option value="+">Topla</option>
        <option value="-">Çıkar</option>
        <option value="*">Çarp</option>
        <option value="/">Böl</option>
    </select>
    <br>
    <input type="submit">
</form>